descript.abstract: This shapefile represents the parcels designated as County Parks in Anoka County. The data was derived from the Anoka County COGO Parcel data layer and an older City Parks layer based on a less accurate parcel dataset. Areas in the southern portion of the County south of Coon Rapids are not based on the COGO data. Theses areas will be updated as more COGO data is available.
